sub

Interface Subscribable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccountActivity, FilterRecord, HeartBeat, MessageGlob, StockRecord, StockRecordParam, TdaAccountActivity, TdaStockRecord

    public interface Subscribable
    Subscribability of a class is enabled by the class implementing the Subscribable interface. Classes that do not implement this interface will not be able to be subscribed to. All subtypes of a Socketable class are themselves Socketable. The subscribable interface has no methods or fields and serves only to identify the semantics of being Subscribable.
    Author:
    Kyle
